</div>]]></content:encoded></item><item><title>泰特幣賣家九龍灣交易被綁架，要求 3000 萬贖金及交易平台密碼</title><link>https://unwire.hk/2021/11/15/coins-30m/fun-tech/?utm_source=rss&amp;utm_medium=rss&amp;utm_campaign=coins-30m</link><dc:creator><![CDATA[Christy]]></dc:creator><pubDate>Mon, 15 Nov 2021 08:09:00 +0000</pubDate><category><![CDATA[科技趣聞]]></category><category><![CDATA[泰特幣]]></category><category><![CDATA[綁架]]></category><guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1071301</guid><description><![CDATA[<p>本月 6 日，一名 39 歲泰特幣賣家與網上買家於九龍灣交易時被綁架，要求其家屬交出 3000 萬金額贖金。於 [&#8230;]</p></p>]]></description><content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>本月 6 日，一名 39 歲泰特幣賣家與網上買家於九龍灣交易時被綁架，要求其家屬交出 3000 萬金額贖金。於綁架後第 6 日，受害人自行由鐵皮屋逃走，現正留醫，暫無生命危險。直至現時為止，共有 6 男 1 女被捕， 7 人介乎 25 至 32 歲，估計仍有 7 至 8 人在逃。</p><p style="text-align: center;"><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/螢幕截圖-2021-11-15-下午 1.26.12.png"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1071303" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/螢幕截圖-2021-11-15-下午 1.26.12-694x332.png" alt="" width="694" height="332" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/螢幕截圖-2021-11-15-下午 1.26.12-694x332.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/螢幕截圖-2021-11-15-下午 1.26.12-1280x612.png 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/螢幕截圖-2021-11-15-下午 1.26.12-768x367.png 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/螢幕截圖-2021-11-15-下午 1.26.12-1536x735.png 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/螢幕截圖-2021-11-15-下午 1.26.12-2048x980.png 2048w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/螢幕截圖-2021-11-15-下午 1.26.12.png 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a> <a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/螢幕截圖-2021-11-15-下午 1.26.33.png"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1071304" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/螢幕截圖-2021-11-15-下午 1.26.33-694x332.png" alt="" width="694" height="332" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/螢幕截圖-2021-11-15-下午 1.26.33-694x332.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/螢幕截圖-2021-11-15-下午 1.26.33-1280x612.png 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/螢幕截圖-2021-11-15-下午 1.26.33-768x367.png 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/螢幕截圖-2021-11-15-下午 1.26.33-1536x735.png 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/螢幕截圖-2021-11-15-下午 1.26.33-2048x980.png 2048w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/螢幕截圖-2021-11-15-下午 1.26.33.png 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a>圖片來源： <a href="https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1619771-20211114.htm">RTHK</a></p><p>西九龍總區刑事部署理高級警司鍾雅倫表示，受害人為 39 歲全職虛擬貨幣賣家。受害人於本月 6 日，與於網上認識並自稱為泰特幣買家在九龍灣交易時被綁走至附近的工廈內。據了解，受害人曾被帶到九龍灣工廈、貨櫃場及大埔南坑村鐵皮屋內禁錮，其間曾多次被疑犯用鐵鎚、鐵櫈及拳腳攻擊至重傷，手腳多處骨折，又要求受害人交出其手機密碼、網上銀行及虛擬貨幣交易平台密碼等資料。最於，受害人於第 6 日時趁負責看守的兩名疑犯在屋外吸煙時，從窗戶逃走，被附近部署的警方發現並帶至醫院留醫，暫無生命危險。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/螢幕截圖-2021-11-15-下午 1.20.55-1.png"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1071306" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/螢幕截圖-2021-11-15-下午 1.20.55-1-694x332.png" alt="" width="694" height="332" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/螢幕截圖-2021-11-15-下午 1.20.55-1-694x332.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/螢幕截圖-2021-11-15-下午 1.20.55-1-1280x612.png 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/螢幕截圖-2021-11-15-下午 1.20.55-1-768x367.png 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/螢幕截圖-2021-11-15-下午 1.20.55-1-1536x735.png 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/螢幕截圖-2021-11-15-下午 1.20.55-1-2048x980.png 2048w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/螢幕截圖-2021-11-15-下午 1.20.55-1.png 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/螢幕截圖-2021-11-15-下午 1.26.47.png"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1071307" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/螢幕截圖-2021-11-15-下午 1.26.47-694x332.png" alt="" width="694" height="332" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/螢幕截圖-2021-11-15-下午 1.26.47-694x332.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/螢幕截圖-2021-11-15-下午 1.26.47-1280x612.png 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/螢幕截圖-2021-11-15-下午 1.26.47-768x367.png 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/螢幕截圖-2021-11-15-下午 1.26.47-1536x735.png 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/螢幕截圖-2021-11-15-下午 1.26.47-2048x980.png 2048w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/螢幕截圖-2021-11-15-下午 1.26.47.png 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p style="text-align: center;">圖片來源： <a href="https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1619771-20211114.htm">RTHK</a></p><p>於綁架期間，疑犯曾多次要求受害人以欠債為由向家人索取贖金，亦因為相信受害人富有而提高贖金金額，由初時 800 萬升至 3000 萬。直至與家人聯絡的第 3 日後，家人才發現異樣而報警。警方表示未查清綁架案所涉及的金額總數，雖然家人未曾繳交贖金，但未能得知受害人網上銀行及虛擬貨幣交易平台的交易記錄，有待查證。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/螢幕截圖-2021-11-15-下午 1.26.59.png"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1071305" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/螢幕截圖-2021-11-15-下午 1.26.59-694x332.png" alt="" width="694" height="332" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/螢幕截圖-2021-11-15-下午 1.26.59-694x332.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/螢幕截圖-2021-11-15-下午 1.26.59-1280x612.png 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/螢幕截圖-2021-11-15-下午 1.26.59-768x367.png 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/螢幕截圖-2021-11-15-下午 1.26.59-1536x735.png 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/螢幕截圖-2021-11-15-下午 1.26.59-2048x980.png 2048w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/螢幕截圖-2021-11-15-下午 1.26.59.png 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p style="text-align: center;">圖片來源： <a href="https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1619771-20211114.htm">RTHK</a></p><p>警方於大埔南坑村部署時發現逃走的受害人並將其救走，隨即將涉事鐵皮屋內的兩名疑犯拘捕。兩日後，警方再拘捕多 5 人。現時共有 6 男 1 女被捕， 7 人介乎 25 至 32 歲，皆有黑社會背景，其中 2 人涉嫌 「綁架」 及「串謀綁架」 被正式落案起訴，於本日 （15 日） 在九龍城裁判法院提堂。</p><p>資料來源：<a href="https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1619771-20211114.htm">RTHK</a></p><p>—</p><p><u>unwire.hk </u>Mewe 專頁 : <a href="https://mewe.com/p/unwirehk"><u>https://mewe.com/p/unwirehk</u></a></p></p><div class="feedflare">
